            <h1>A web platform for classroom communities.</h1>
            <p>Whiteboard is an interactive learning platform that revolutionizes the way educators and students connect in a classroom setting. Educators can quickly and easily receive live feedback from students, or create dynamic quizzes and polls with Whiteboard's clicker functionality. Whiteboard's interface was designed with desktop and mobile users in mind, and can be used from any device with a web browser and internet connection. We also did away with login pages and accounts all-together; both educators and students can create and join sessions with just a few clicks of the mouse or a few taps on the screen.</p>
